headline: Maryland Businesses Announce Key Innovations, Local Investments, and Community Giving
summary: The Maryland Marketing Partnership, which helps drive Maryland's branding and marketing efforts to attract businesses, create jobs, and grow the state's economy, today shared a summary of the latest news from companies and organizations that invest in the partnership.

headline: M&T Bank Ranks No. 1 Among 7(a) SBA Lenders in Its Footprint*
summary: M&T Bank (NYSE: MTB) was the largest 7(a) Small Business Administration (SBA) lender in its footprint by units in Fiscal Year 2025 and, for the 17th consecutive year, ranked among the nation's top 10 Small Business Administration (SBA) 7(a) lenders.
